  "title": "Local Transport Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop\n     new business opportunities for <strong>local transport and trucking services</strong></li><li>Manage\n     and grow existing customer accounts</li><li>Prepare\n     quotations for local deliveries, container movements, and adhoc jobs</li><li>Achieve\n     monthly sales targets and KPIs</li><li>Coordinate\n     with operations and drivers to ensure smooth job execution</li><li>Handle\n     customer enquiries, follow-ups, and service issues</li><li>Monitor\n     market rates and competitor activities</li><li><strong>Requirements </strong></li><li>Minimum <strong>1–3 years’ experience</strong> in local transport, trucking, cranes or logistics sales</li><li>Good\n     understanding of Singapore road transport operations<br />\n     (e.g. container haulage, loose cargo, last-mile delivery)</li><li>Strong\n     communication and negotiation skills</li><li>Target-driven,\n     self-motivated, and customer-oriented</li><li>Proficient\n     in MS Office and basic CRM systems<br /></li></ul>",
